  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion criteria

          -  Patients undergoing multiple tooth extractions aged b/w 35- 70 years and with INR
             values ≤ 3.5 (1-3.5)

          -  If present, sugar level should be under control

        Exclusion criteria

          -  Patients undergoing a single tooth or multiple extractions in same quadrant; and those
             with an allergy to seafood.
      </textblock>
